{"article_id":"f28GOBlqPRPG2Pvu","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"Democrats , Planned Parenthood and others on the left are trying to generate pseudo-hysteria","depth":5},{"id":1,"text":"by falsely demonizing Judge Brett Kavanaugh as being anti-woman in the days","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"leading up to the Senate confirmation hearing Tuesday on his nomination to the U.S. Supreme Court .","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"While trying to portray themselves as champions of womankind ,","depth":5},{"id":4,"text":"those","depth":7},{"id":5,"text":"fighting the nomination of Kavanaugh","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"are instead insulting the intelligence of women and men with their absurd attacks .","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"The Kavanaugh opponents are trying to stir up uncontrolled and extreme emotions","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"relating to the Roe v. Wade","depth":7},{"id":9,"text":"- the 1973 Supreme Court decision","depth":8},{"id":10,"text":"legalizing abortion nationwide -","depth":8},{"id":11,"text":"in their campaign","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"to keep Kavanaugh off the nation ' s highest court .","depth":6},{"id":13,"text":"No one can credibly claim","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"that Kavanaugh is not qualified","depth":9},{"id":15,"text":"to sit on the Supreme Court .","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"He ' s been a judge on the U.S . Circuit Court of Appeals for the District of Columbia since 2006 .","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"He has a sterling record","depth":10},{"id":18,"text":"since graduating from Yale Law School in 1990 ,","depth":10},{"id":19,"text":"including serving as a Supreme Court clerk , a lawyer in the White House Counsel ' s Office , and White House staff secretary for President George W. Bush .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh has shown beyond a shadow of a doubt that has an intentional , extraordinary record","depth":8},{"id":21,"text":"of helping women .","depth":8},{"id":22,"text":"So","depth":8},{"id":23,"text":"instead of examining his qualifications or judicial record ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"those opposed to Kavanaugh are working overtime","depth":10},{"id":25,"text":"to smear his reputation with false charges .","depth":10},{"id":26,"text":"And in addition to trying to derail the judge ' s nomination ,","depth":6},{"id":27,"text":"those opposing him are engaged in a cynical propaganda campaign of political fundraising .","depth":7},{"id":28,"text":"They are urging donors to give money to Democrats","depth":8},{"id":29,"text":"to defeat Republicans in the November midterm elections","depth":9},{"id":30,"text":"in order to block the confirmation of future judicial nominees","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"advanced by President Trump .","depth":10},{"id":32,"text":"The campaign","depth":8},{"id":33,"text":"to keep Kavanaugh off the Supreme Court","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"has taken some strange and frankly disgusting turns .","depth":7},{"id":35,"text":"For example , a lame Planned Parenthood video ,","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"made with the help of the group ' s friends at \" Funny or Die , \"","depth":10},{"id":37,"text":"tries to inject humor into the deadly serious topic of abortion .","depth":9},{"id":38,"text":"Excuse me for not laughing .","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"It used to be that abortion was discussed in a sober manner , even by those on the left .","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"Remember when they claimed","depth":11},{"id":41,"text":"they actually wanted abortion to be \" safe , legal , and rare ? \"","depth":11},{"id":42,"text":"Sadly , those days are long gone .","depth":9},{"id":43,"text":"Now the pro-abortion forces are trivializing the pain and struggle of women","depth":10},{"id":44,"text":"confronted with the terrible choice","depth":11},{"id":45,"text":"of whether to have an abortion","depth":12},{"id":46,"text":"or instead grant their unborn child the right","depth":13},{"id":47,"text":"to live a full life .","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"In the Planned Parenthood video ,","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"which is designed","depth":14},{"id":50,"text":"to mobilize opposition to Kavanaugh ' s nomination ,","depth":14},{"id":51,"text":"an actor","depth":15},{"id":52,"text":"who is playing the part of a dumb and clueless conservative","depth":15},{"id":53,"text":"addresses women","depth":14},{"id":54,"text":"and says :","depth":14},{"id":55,"text":"\" Basically , I ' m here","depth":15},{"id":56,"text":"to explain to you , as a man ,","depth":16},{"id":57,"text":"that you ' re wrong about Brett Kavanaugh . \"","depth":16},{"id":58,"text":"Ha !","depth":13},{"id":59,"text":"See what they did there ?","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"Because only men support Kavanaugh ,","depth":15},{"id":61,"text":"you see .","depth":15},{"id":62,"text":"So clever .","depth":12},{"id":63,"text":"The joke continues for what seems like an eternity ,","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"and the faux-conservative actor points out","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"that Kavanaugh will be good for women","depth":14},{"id":66,"text":"because he has a \" female wife , female mother , and female mother-in-law . \"","depth":14},{"id":67,"text":"The actor even says","depth":14},{"id":68,"text":"\" ladies , let me talk to you like a lady \"","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"and switches to a falsetto voice .","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"Thankfully , he doesn ' t put on a wig and a dress for added comedic effect .","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"They make millions with these jokes .","depth":7},{"id":72,"text":"They kill at the Oscars .","depth":7},{"id":73,"text":"But millions of women recognize this nonsense as phony , not funny .","depth":7},{"id":74,"text":"They reject the assumption","depth":8},{"id":75,"text":"that those of us","depth":11},{"id":76,"text":"who support the right to life for the unborn","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"are anti-woman ,","depth":10},{"id":78,"text":"and that pro-life women are traitors to the cause of women ' s rights .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Instead of engaging conservative women in a respectful way","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"and debating the record of Judge Kavanaugh ,","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"opponents of his nomination prefer to mock the pain of millions of women as one big joke .","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"For example , NARAL Pro-Choice Oregon has partnered with an ice cream shop","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"to sell abortion-themed ice cream .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"The oh-so clever flavor is called \" Rocky Roe v. Wade . \"","depth":8},{"id":85,"text":"Why ?","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"Because the pro-abortion groups want women to celebrate abortions","depth":9},{"id":87,"text":"and promote them to girls .","depth":9},{"id":88,"text":"Concerned Women for America","depth":9},{"id":89,"text":"( CWA ) ,","depth":9},{"id":90,"text":"the organization","depth":9},{"id":91,"text":"I lead ,","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"has thousands of members around the country","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"who support Judge Kavanaugh","depth":7},{"id":94,"text":"because he is a man of integrity","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"who will uphold the Constitution","depth":10},{"id":96,"text":"as written ,","depth":10},{"id":97,"text":"instead of bending it","depth":11},{"id":98,"text":"and giving it new meaning","depth":11},{"id":99,"text":"to promote his personal preferences .","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"I have written about Kavanaugh ' s substantive record and why we can trust him .","depth":7},{"id":101,"text":"Our \" Women for Kavanaugh \" bus tour visited seven key states","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"( Iowa , Indiana , West Virginia , Missouri , North Dakota , Alabama , and Florida )","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"to win the support of senators for Kavanaugh .","depth":9},{"id":104,"text":"We have felt overwhelming support for the judge from women in those states and elsewhere","depth":9},{"id":105,"text":"once they look at his record .","depth":9},{"id":106,"text":"But the Hollywood elites and others on the left will not engage conservative women in a meaningful way .","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"So many of them live in a bubble","depth":9},{"id":108,"text":"where everyone thinks alike","depth":10},{"id":109,"text":"and everyone","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"who doesn ' t","depth":12},{"id":111,"text":"is dismissed outright .","depth":11},{"id":112,"text":"Their idea","depth":9},{"id":113,"text":"of engaging conservative women","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"is \" comedian \" Michelle Wolf ' s shameful treatment of Sarah Huckabee Sanders at the White House Correspondents ' Dinner in April , to the cheers of the liberal media .","depth":8},{"id":115,"text":"With this myopic view of women , Kavanaugh ' s opponents can say ridiculous things","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"- like claiming","depth":9},{"id":117,"text":"that anyone","depth":11},{"id":118,"text":"who supports Judge Kavanaugh","depth":11},{"id":119,"text":"is \" complicit in evil. \"","depth":10},{"id":120,"text":"They can talk about \" back-alley abortions \"","depth":9},{"id":121,"text":"and make absurd claims","depth":10},{"id":122,"text":"that Kavanaugh \" has a long history","depth":11},{"id":123,"text":"of not caring for women. \"","depth":11},{"id":124,"text":"They know","depth":10},{"id":125,"text":"it is all lies ,","depth":10},{"id":126,"text":"but they are hoping","depth":10},{"id":127,"text":"they will galvanize liberal support .","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"American women are not stupid .","depth":7},{"id":129,"text":"Millions are seeing clearly","depth":9},{"id":130,"text":"that we are being told lies about President Trump ' s Supreme Court nominee .","depth":9},{"id":131,"text":"We realize","depth":9},{"id":132,"text":"that anyone","depth":12},{"id":133,"text":"nominated by this president to the Supreme Court","depth":12},{"id":134,"text":"- no matter how qualified -","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"would face a torrent of opposition .","depth":10},{"id":136,"text":"Judge Kavanaugh has shown beyond a shadow of a doubt that has an intentional , extraordinary record","depth":7},{"id":137,"text":"of helping women .","depth":7},{"id":138,"text":"In a letter to the Senate Judiciary Committee , all the women","depth":9},{"id":139,"text":"who served Kavanaugh as law clerks","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"( unless prevented","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"because of \" current or pending employment \" )","depth":11},{"id":142,"text":"wrote","depth":8},{"id":143,"text":"that he \" has been one of the strongest advocates in the federal judiciary for women lawyers . \"","depth":7},{"id":144,"text":"Even many on the left are not buying what the radical left is doing with the nomination of such a well-qualified nominee .","depth":6},{"id":145,"text":"Liberal feminist lawyer Lisa Blatt ,","depth":10},{"id":146,"text":"who has argued more cases before the Supreme Court than any other woman ,","depth":10},{"id":147,"text":"wrote for Politico :","depth":9},{"id":148,"text":"\" Sometimes a superstar is just a superstar .","depth":9},{"id":149,"text":"That is the case with Judge Brett Kavanaugh ,","depth":11},{"id":150,"text":"who had long been considered the most qualified nominee for the Supreme Court","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"if Republicans secured the White House .","depth":12},{"id":152,"text":"The Senate should confirm him . \"","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"Blatt has personal experience in her law career","depth":10},{"id":154,"text":"working with Kavanaugh","depth":10},{"id":155,"text":"that gives her a good perspective on the type of justice","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"he will be .","depth":10},{"id":157,"text":"Blatt had to admit , though ,","depth":11},{"id":158,"text":"that \" my friends on the left will criticize me","depth":12},{"id":159,"text":"for speaking up for Kavanaugh. \"","depth":12},{"id":160,"text":"Yes .","depth":10},{"id":161,"text":"She is not toeing the liberal line ,","depth":10},{"id":162,"text":"and there are real consequences for this .","depth":10},{"id":163,"text":"Here ' s the bottom line :","depth":3},{"id":164,"text":"Donald Trump is the duly elected president of the United States ,","depth":4},{"id":165,"text":"even though that continues to drive his opponents crazy .","depth":4},{"id":166,"text":"He has carried out his duty","depth":4},{"id":167,"text":"to nominate an eminently qualified judge","depth":5},{"id":168,"text":"to serve on the Supreme Court .","depth":5},{"id":169,"text":"The Senate should do its job","depth":4},{"id":170,"text":"and confirm Judge Brett Kavanaugh","depth":5},{"id":171,"text":"because he will clearly be an outstanding member of the United States Supreme Court .","depth":5}],"relations":[{"parent":343,"left":334,"right":342,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":334,"left":203,"right":333,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":203,"left":178,"right":202,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":178,"left":174,"right":177,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":174,"left":0,"right":173,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":173,"left":1,"right":2,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":177,"left":3,"right":176,"relation":"adversative","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":176,"left":175,"right":6,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":175,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":202,"left":183,"right":201,"relation":"explanation","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":183,"left":181,"right":182,"relation":"same-unit","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":181,"left":7,"right":180,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":180,"left":8,"right":179,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":179,"left":9,"right":10,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":182,"left":11,"right":12,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":195,"right":200,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":195,"left":189,"right":194,"relation":"explanation","nucl